    <summary>Stealth TUI YouTube audio player - stream music while looking productive</summary>
    <description>
wrkmon is a terminal-based YouTube audio player that runs completely hidden in the background.

## Features
- Search and stream YouTube audio
- No visible windows - completely stealth
- TUI interface with keyboard controls
- Queue management with shuffle/repeat
- Play history and playlists
- Cross-platform (Windows, macOS, Linux)

## Usage
Simply run `wrkmon` in your terminal to start the TUI interface.

## Controls
- F1-F4: Switch views (Search, Queue, History, Playlists)
- F5: Play/Pause
- F9: Stop
- F10: Add to queue
- /: Focus search
